35
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,279
  I believed you! 

36
00:05:09,279 --> 00:05:13,880
  I believed you! I believed you! 

37
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:28,119
  Sister. 

38
00:06:29,847 --> 00:06:31,347
 What's the matter? 

39
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:35,040
 Brother, I'm scared. 

40
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,639
 It's all right. I'm here. 

41
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:39,139
 Don't be scared. 

42
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,779
 Come, you can sleep with me. 

43
