Brother, I want to remind you.

45
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:34,360
She was drunk and acted out of character. Those words didn't mean anything.

46
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:37,043
The problem between you two is still there.

47
00:08:38,459 --> 00:08:39,959
I know.

48
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:42,659
