59
00:09:20,159 --> 00:09:23,939
But she's here, so I have to get her.

60
00:09:23,939 --> 00:09:25,699
She's here?

61
00:09:25,699 --> 00:09:29,583
Where? How come I didn't see her?

62
00:09:32,206 --> 00:09:35,039
All right. Go to school.

63
