89
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:46,240
If you wish to go, then go.

90
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:50,240
However, just this time.

91
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,559
This one time.

92
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:55,589
No matter what,

93
00:10:55,589 --> 00:10:58,559
