139
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,140
Aunt Zhai's cooking is delicious.

140
00:16:53,919 --> 00:16:55,720
How's the food at the station canteen?

141
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,399
Not too bad.

142
00:16:57,399 --> 00:16:58,799
Yours?

143
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:00,879
So-so.

144
00:17:00,879 --> 00:17:02,679
It's not very good.

145
00:17:26,659 --> 00:17:28,559
Have some water.

146
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,860
It smells good.

147
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,640
You must be hungry.

148
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:46,040
It's almost done.

149
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:48,620
Okay.

150
00:19:18,359 --> 00:19:19,859
Xu Qin.

151
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:24,259
Do you remember...

152
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,841
what you said yesterday?

153
00:19:31,979 --> 00:19:35,609
I remember parts of it, but not everything.

154
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,480
You said...

155
00:19:39,799 --> 00:19:41,932
you'd never come toward me again.

156
00:19:42,839 --> 00:19:46,240
Do you remember that part?

157
00:19:54,559 --> 00:19:56,639
You're not drunk now, right?

158
00:20:00,319 --> 00:20:02,019
So are you...

159
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:05,566
still going to say that now?

160
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,839
I don't know.

161
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,839
What if I go toward you?

162
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:29,739
Can you wait?

163
00:20:40,319 --> 00:20:42,408
Waiting without certainty,

164
00:20:43,119 --> 00:20:45,182
even I feel bad for you.

165
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:52,580
I don't know...

166
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:56,179
what I should do right now.

167
00:21:00,759 --> 00:21:03,599
I don't know how to ask you...

168
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,180
or ask myself.

169
00:21:06,799 --> 00:21:08,820
I also don't know...

170
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:13,640
how to face you or my family.

171
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:16,180
- I... 
 - I know you're scared.

172
00:21:17,619 --> 00:21:19,680
I just want you to know.

173
00:21:20,212 --> 00:21:22,240
If you're determined enough,

174
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:24,675
I will bear whatever happens after.

175
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:28,319
If you are brave enough,

176
00:21:28,319 --> 00:21:30,450
then I'll shoulder it.

177
00:21:42,699 --> 00:21:44,299
But I get it.

178
00:21:45,599 --> 00:21:47,559
The words sound nice,

179
00:21:48,799 --> 00:21:50,699
but they're useless.

180
00:21:55,079 --> 00:21:57,440
I don't have enough courage.

181
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,560
To be honest,

182
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:07,060
I feel bad that I put you

183
00:22:07,759 --> 00:22:09,679
in this predicament.

184
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:13,654
I know your good intention.

185
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:34,119
What I can promise you is to treat you well.

186
00:22:34,119 --> 00:22:35,960
I'll be good to you every day.

187
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:39,279
I'll never betray you. I'll not be indifferent.

188
00:22:39,279 --> 00:22:42,219
I'll do everything I can to give you a better life.

189
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:45,920
What I cannot guarantee

190
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:50,799
is whether or not my commitment to you fits your

191
00:22:50,799 --> 00:22:53,060
or your family's requirements.

192
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:56,940
I know you're in a difficult position.

193
00:22:58,079 --> 00:22:59,879
I also know...

194
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:02,948
that if we do get together...

195
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:07,480
you'd be aggrieved.

196
00:23:08,839 --> 00:23:10,539
I understand that.

197
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:14,420
But...

198
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:23,340
you can't keep barging into my life recklessly like this.

199
00:23:26,319 --> 00:23:28,019
Be together...

200
00:23:29,359 --> 00:23:31,585
or never see each other again.

201
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:35,156
Make your choice.

202
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:49,000
 Did I not tell you? 

203
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:52,019
 Stay away from those shady people. 

204
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:55,179
 You don't have any self respect at all. 

205
00:24:55,799 --> 00:24:58,179
 If you insist on being with him, 

206
00:24:59,039 --> 00:25:03,620
 then forget about attending the university. 

207
00:25:05,319 --> 00:25:08,199
 You can discard this family, too. 

208
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:12,079
 From now on, you can't call me "Mom" anymore. 

209
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,520
 Mom. 

210
00:25:18,839 --> 00:25:20,339
 Qin Qin. 

211
00:25:21,153 --> 00:25:23,457
 Please listen to me. 

212
00:25:23,457 --> 00:25:25,881
 I only want the best for you. 

213
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:29,580
 I'm willing to give you the world. 

214
00:25:30,839 --> 00:25:32,539
 But if... 

215
00:25:34,039 --> 00:25:38,519
 you're going to act willfully and disregard this family, 

216
00:25:40,519 --> 00:25:44,599
 then I'm going to find a way to send you away. 

217
00:25:45,279 --> 00:25:49,279
 There's no use pleading to your father or brother. 

218
00:25:49,279 --> 00:25:52,859
 I will do what I said. 

219
00:25:52,859 --> 00:25:54,359
 Mom. 

220
00:25:59,559 --> 00:26:01,259
 Qin Qin. 

221
00:26:02,828 --> 00:26:05,640
 His parents aren't good people. 

222
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,240
 What do you expect from their child? 

223
00:26:09,939 --> 00:26:12,240
 I'm truly disappointed in you. 

224
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:15,580
 You break my heart 

225
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:18,300
 because of a guy like that? 

226
00:26:19,839 --> 00:26:22,559
 The care and love I gave you all these years... 

227
00:26:23,759 --> 00:26:27,000
 has all been in vain. 

228
00:26:35,559 --> 00:26:37,159
 Mom. 

229
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:40,219
 I'll do as you say. 

