00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:49,530
♫  Are you those drifting clouds, one after another?  ♫

238
00:28:49,530 --> 00:28:53,430
♫  I wish I were the wind passing by you  ♫

239
00:28:53,430 --> 00:28:58,300
♫  Unable to resist falling into your eyes again  ♫

240
00:29:00,210 --> 00:29:06,500
♫  Why can't I get around this unchangeable summer?  ♫

