00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:21,390
♫  Those words that I didn't have the courage to say  ♫

243
00:29:29,835 --> 00:29:31,759
Why are you here so early?

244
00:29:31,759 --> 00:29:33,960
I'm picking you up to go to work.

245
00:29:33,960 --> 00:29:35,660
Have you eaten?

246
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:38,460
Yes.

247
00:29:41,328 --> 00:29:42,819
Let's go.

248
00:29:50,799 --> 00:29:55,960
 Actually, you didn't have to take me home yesterday. 

249
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:58,580
Even if you didn't remind me,

250
00:29:58,580 --> 00:30:01,058
I wouldn't dare resist.

251
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:04,700
What are you scared of?

252
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,444
Do you think because I'm an adult,

253
00:30:07,444 --> 00:30:11,460
I've strengthened my wings and will leave everything behind by flying away?

254
00:30:13,519 --> 00:30:16,860
Do you know how an animal trainer tames animals?

255
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:20,639
While the animal is young,

256
00:30:21,240 --> 00:30:24,979
they beat it, starve it, and lock it up.

257
00:30:24,979 --> 00:30:28,860
But they also adore it, feed it, and care for it.

258
00:30:31,279 --> 00:30:34,839
When the animal grows up and has more power,

259
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:40,340
when they see the whip and food bowl, they'll no longer resist.

260
00:30:41,359 --> 00:30:43,439
It no longer dares to return to the wild.

261
00:30:44,319 --> 00:30:46,300
All of you say

262
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:48,899
he's not good enough for me.

263
00:30:50,119 --> 00:30:52,919
But the fact is, I'm not good enough for him.

264
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:56,340
When I'm with him,

265
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,720
I feel like...

266
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:02,399
I could hurt him everywhere I go.

267
00:31:04,530 --> 00:31:07,201
Because the truth is, I'm a despicable person.

268
00:31:07,201 --> 00:31:09,270
I want everything,

269
00:31:10,239 --> 00:31:12,499
but I'm scared of losing everything.

270
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:17,680
I want Dad, Mom, and you.

271
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,359
I also want Song Yan.

272
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,460
I...

273
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:29,639
I don't have the courage or the guts.

274
00:31:30,559 --> 00:31:34,219
I can't bear to face anything. I only know to run away.

275
00:31:36,119 --> 00:31:38,259
I'm incapable of love,

276
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:41,079
nor do I have the right to love.

277
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:45,640
I don't deserve love from anyone.

278
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,649
Let's leave the country.

279
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:03,319
Qin Qin, let's go abroad together.

280
00:32:03,319 --> 00:32:05,520
We'll never return, okay?

281
00:32:13,759 --> 00:32:15,659
Goodbye, Brother.

282
00:32:43,319 --> 00:32:46,279
Well? The air is good, right?

283
00:32:46,279 --> 00:32:49,240
You should come outdoors more often.

284
00:32:50,119 --> 00:32:52,920
You really know what the hospital staff needs, Mrs. Meng.

285
00:32:52,920 --> 00:32:55,440
 We're overwhelmed by the smell of disinfectant in the hospital. 

286
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:58,019
 It's nice to be out enjoying the fresh air. 

287
00:32:58,019 --> 00:33:00,759
 Assistant Director Liu, I was going to ask you. 

288
00:33:00,759 --> 00:33:03,680
My child has been working at the hospital for a while now.

289
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,983
How is it?

290
00:33:04,983 --> 00:33:08,322
Are the seniors and professors happy with her performance?

291
00:33:08,322 --> 00:33:10,400
Very pleased.

292
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:13,359
Junior Dr. Xu is serious about work.

293
00:33:13,359 --> 00:33:15,319
And she's compassionate with patients.

294
00:33:15,319 --> 00:33:19,180
The hospital has chosen her to be a key candidate for promotion.

295
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:23,720
I thank you for the guidance on my daughter's behalf.

296
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:25,420
It's my pleasure.

297
00:33:30,959 --> 00:33:32,559
Department Chief Xu.

298
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:37,413
May I know why my interview application was rejected?

299
00:33:40,060 --> 00:33:42,979
Trying to get a promotion through connections doesn't work with me.

300
00:33:42,979 --> 00:33:44,620
Go back and tell your family.

301
00:33:44,620 --> 00:33:46,825
Quit asking Assistant Director Liu to contact me.

302
00:33:46,825 --> 00:33:52,599
My medical team needs only young people who have a sincere passion for the job,

303
00:33:52,599 --> 00:33:58,119
but not someone who thinks they can get what they want by taking shortcuts.

304
00:33:58,119 --> 00:34:02,179
But you know I have the best skills among the young doctors.

305
00:34:05,210 --> 00:34:07,640
A doctor needs to have comprehensive skills.

306
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:09,981
I don't think you're the best at that.

307
00:34:09,981 --> 00:34:12,079
If you talk about being arrogant,

308
00:34:12,079 --> 00:34:13,974
you might be the strongest.

309
00:34:15,219 --> 00:34:16,480
Department Chief Xu,

310
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:19,639
honestly, I believe Dr. Xu has what it takes.

311
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:21,559
Maybe you should reconsider.

312
00:34:22,472 --> 00:34:25,992
   

313
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,438
- Xiao Yang. 
 - Yes.

314
00:34:31,438 --> 00:34:33,360
Did you hear anything about the new instructor?

315
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:35,960
Is he easy to get along with? What kind of character is he?

316
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:38,400
I don't know if he's easy to get along with.

317
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:40,920
But if Brother Yan can get along with him, then I can, too.

318
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:44,360
No need to think so much. We'll know when he arrives this afternoon.

319
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:47,039
I heard he came from the headquarters.

320
00:34:47,039 --> 00:34:49,159
He comes from a prominent family.

321
00:34:49,159 --> 00:34:51,400
Why isn't he sitting in an air-conditioned office

322
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:53,579
but is choosing to come here instead?

323
00:34:53,579 --> 00:34:57,164
I reckon he decided to get a jumpstart and gold plating. 
  (T/N: enhance this resume ) 

324
00:34:57,164 --> 00:35:00,979
I won't be surprised if he doesn't last long.

325
00:35:00,979 --> 00:35:02,960
Knowing our captain's temper,

326
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:06,519
who can say whether he'll get gold plated or skinned?

327
00:35:06,519 --> 00:35:10,600
Honestly, I miss Brother Jun.

328
00:35:11,360 --> 00:35:13,379
An instructor like Brother Jun?

329
00:35:14,039 --> 00:35:16,039
There won't be a second one.

330
00:35:17,679 --> 00:35:20,480
In the past, we were tired of his nagging.

331
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:23,999
Now that it's quiet, I'm not used to it.

332
00:35:25,519 --> 00:35:26,960
Brother Chi.

333
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:29,800
Brother Yi. The new instructor is about to arrive.

334
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:31,920
- Not this afternoon? 
 - They pushed it forward?

335
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:34,519
Speak of the devil. Let's go welcome him.

336
00:35:34,519 --> 00:35:35,767
All right! Stop what you're doing!

337
00:35:35,767 --> 00:35:37,280
Let's go greet the new instructor!

338
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:39,099
- Let's go. 
 - Okay.

339
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:53,320
Hello, Captain Song.

340
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:54,599
Long time no see.

341
00:35:54,599 --> 00:35:58,519
You said I could look for you at Shili Tai Fire and Rescue Station.

342
00:36:01,079 --> 00:36:02,479
Hello.

343
00:36:03,629 --> 00:36:04,760
Where's the new instructor?

344
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:06,460
I'm the one.

345
00:36:12,679 --> 00:36:14,699
This is my assignment order.

346
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,280
You are Jiang Yu?

347
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:23,748
I guess you don't remember me from last time.

348
00:36:23,748 --> 00:36:26,840
Then allow me to formally introduce myself.

349
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,119
My name is Jiang Yu.

350
00:36:28,119 --> 00:36:30,760
I'm the new instructor based at Shili Tai Fire and Rescue Station.

351
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:32,920
Starting today, I'll be joining the team.

352
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,535
Pleased to meet everyone.

353
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:41,800
- Yang Chi. 
 - Here.

354
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:44,239
What are you people doing just standing there?

355
00:36:44,239 --> 00:36:45,960
Are you all electric poles or what?

356
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:48,919
- Hello, Sir. 
 - Welcome, welcome.

357
00:36:50,079 --> 00:36:51,519
- Don't mention it. 
 - Thanks for coming.

358
00:36:51,519 --> 00:36:54,541
Don't mention it, Guys. I can manage, yes.

359
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:59,599
The instructor has a kind face. He should be friendly.

360
00:36:59,599 --> 00:37:02,519
But why does it seem like there's tension between him and Captain?

361
00:37:02,519 --> 00:37:03,719
Brother.

362
00:37:03,719 --> 00:37:06,619
Right now, could you just zip that big mouth of yours?

363
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:09,090
Let's go.

364
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,219
Close the door.

365
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:19,410
   

366
00:37:29,059 --> 00:37:33,059
Thank you for coming to the interview.

367
00:37:33,921 --> 00:37:36,781
I hope there's another opportunity to see you again.

368
00:37:40,599 --> 00:37:43,920
- Thanks, Sir. 
 - Keep up the good work, okay?

369
00:37:47,159 --> 00:37:49,999
All right, that's all for today.

370
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:52,539
Department Chief Xu.

371
00:37:52,539 --> 00:37:54,407
What are you doing here?

372
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,559
Your name is not on the list of interviewees.

373
00:37:57,559 --> 00:37:59,559
I'm sorry. I wish to fight for my spot.

374
00:37:59,559 --> 00:38:02,320
The interview session has concluded.

375
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,119
Please take a look at my application

376
00:38:04,119 --> 00:38:07,159
before you decide whether I deserve a chance.

377
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:11,519
I believe that a hospital is where professionalism is valued.

378
00:38:11,519 --> 00:38:13,920
If you think I'm lacking in certain areas outside of my expertise,

379
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:16,959
please tell me so that I can learn from you.

380
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:21,600
Are you mocking me?

381
00:38:22,599 --> 00:38:25,099
No, Sir. Don't get me wrong.

382
00:38:26,199 --> 00:38:27,719
Fine.

383
00:38:27,719 --> 00:38:30,819
Tell me, then. Why do you want to be a doctor?

384
00:38:34,559 --> 00:38:36,000
Don't be nervous.

385
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,944
Think before you answer.

386
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:43,620
Because...

387
00:38:46,039 --> 00:38:48,159
the job is secure.

388
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:02,719
I've got to hand it to Dr. Xu.

389
00:39:02,719 --> 00:39:07,239
Knowing how the director is, she still dared to test his patience.

390
00:39:07,239 --> 00:39:08,960
I heard from the Assistant Director,

391
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:10,900
when Dr. Xu answered the first question like that,

392
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:13,360
she almost passed out and thought it was over.

393
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:16,440
Who would've thought she could pass the interview in the end?

394
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:17,639
Odd, isn't it?

395
00:39:17,639 --> 00:39:22,099
What to do? She has the ability. You can't fault her for being smug.

396
00:39:22,810 --> 00:39:24,000
It's going to get interesting.

397
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:27,159
She's now on the same team as the ultra-smug Yang Si Jia.

398
00:39:27,159 --> 00:39:29,679
Let's wait and see what drama unfolds.

399
00:39:30,679 --> 00:39:32,660
Am I smug?

400
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:34,560
Dr. Yang.

401
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:38,679
Where's my phone?

402
00:39:38,679 --> 00:39:41,719
- Where's my phone? 
 - Maybe you left it in the lobby.

403
00:39:41,719 --> 00:39:43,414
I'll go look for it.

404
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:54,440
Dr. Xu!

405
00:39:55,679 --> 00:39:57,440
Welcome to the team.

406
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:59,380
Let's shake hands.

407
00:39:59,380 --> 00:40:02,239
I just washed my hands, so I won't shake hands.

408
00:40:04,559 --> 00:40:06,559
Well, here's a gentle reminder.

409
00:40:06,559 --> 00:40:08,106
Department Chief Xu is very strict.

410
00:40:08,106 --> 00:40:11,440
Be prepared to suffer while working under him.

411
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:13,000
Being strict is a good thing.

412
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:15,280
I don't think enduring is a form of suffering.

413
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:28,880
 Sir, upstairs is where the dormitory and entertainment space are. 
   

414
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:32,000
Through the courtyard, we'll come to the canteen.

415
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:34,099
It's so big.

416
00:40:34,099 --> 00:40:35,679
The fire station has a dog?

417
00:40:35,679 --> 00:40:37,800
Yes, our captain took him in.

418
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:39,039
- What's its name? 
 - Xiao Meng.

419
00:40:39,039 --> 00:40:43,519
Xiao Meng is well-trained by our captain, almost as good as a professional K9.

420
00:40:44,519 --> 00:40:46,780
Hello, Xiao Meng.

421
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:48,480
- Sir! 
 - Why did it bite?

422
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:50,760
- It's okay. Calm down. It doesn't bite. 
 - It doesn't?

423
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:53,239
- Sir. 
 - That's enough. Down.

424
00:40:53,239 --> 00:40:55,480
Let me show you the canteen. It's that way.

425
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:57,519
Nice to meet you, Master Meng.

426
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:21,380
Captain Song.

427
00:41:21,380 --> 00:41:24,115
Yang Chi gave me a tour of the station already.

428
00:41:24,115 --> 00:41:26,719
I have some things I'd like to know more about from you.

429
00:41:26,719 --> 00:41:27,800
You should rest early.

